<emphasis box="[1191,1210,1796,1817]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">
<collectionCode box="[1191,1206,1796,1817]" country="Sweden" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15668" name="Department of Botany, Swedish Museum of Natural History" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" type="Herbarium">S</collectionCode>
.
</emphasis>
ser. 
<emphasis box="[1252,1392,1796,1817]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Racemuliferae</emphasis>
to the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Miller" authorityYear="1754" box="[321,413,1832,1853]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Jacobaea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="8" pageNumber="137" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[321,413,1832,1853]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="137">Jacobaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
than to transfer it to the genus as a series or section to avoid making any new combination.
